snippet.title: Johnny Depp's Friend Reveals Amber Heard About Faking Injuries
snippet.description:
In this video we’ll talk about Josh Richman, an old friend of Johnny Depp revealing Amber Heard has a history of faking injuries. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
___________________________________________

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard continue to exchange accusations as Depp pushes forward with his $50 million defamation claim against Heard. He was suing Heard for a Washington Post op-ed in which she talked about being a domestic viole nce survivor. While she didn’t name Depp, the allusion was clear, and Depp blames the loss of several lucrative acting gigs, including his role in the Pirates of the Caribbean franchise, on it.
